### Get all books
GET http://localhost:3000/books
Accept: application/json

### Create book
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dune",
  "published": "2005-08-02",
  "isbn": "9780441013593",
  "authorId": 3
}

### Update existing book (replace id with real)
PUT http://localhost:3000/books/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dune (Dune chronicles book #1)",
  "published": "2005-08-02",
  "isbn": "9780441013593",
  "authorId": 3
}

### Delete book (replace id with a real)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/books/4



